<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Frequently Asked
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Questions
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Everything you need to know about MedGemma Health
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-10" data-controller="accordion">
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
        <button class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left" data-action="click->accordion#toggle">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">How accurate is MedGemma's AI diagnosis?</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-plus text-blue-600 transform transition-transform duration-300"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="mt-4 hidden overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out opacity-0" data-accordion-target="content">
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            MedGemma's AI diagnostic system has been validated with over 95% accuracy in controlled studies. It uses Google's MedGemma large language model, which has been trained on millions of medical cases and the latest medical research. However, our AI is designed as a supporting tool, and all diagnoses are reviewed by licensed healthcare professionals before final recommendations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
        <button class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left" data-action="click->accordion#toggle">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Is my medical data secure and private?</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-plus text-blue-600 transform transition-transform duration-300"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="mt-4 hidden overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out opacity-0" data-accordion-target="content">
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Absolutely. MedGemma Health is fully HIPAA compliant and uses end-to-end encryption for all data. Your medical information is stored on secure servers with strict access controls. We never sell or share your personal health information with third parties without your explicit consent. You maintain complete ownership of your data and can request its deletion at any time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
        <button class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left" data-action="click->accordion#toggle">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Can I use insurance with MedGemma?</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-plus text-blue-600 transform transition-transform duration-300"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="mt-4 hidden overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out opacity-0" data-accordion-target="content">
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Yes, MedGemma Health works with most major insurance providers including BlueCross BlueShield, Aetna, Cigna, UnitedHealthcare, and Medicare. During registration, you can add your insurance information, and we'll verify your coverage. For telehealth consultations, the same co-pays typically apply as for in-person visits. We also offer affordable self-pay options.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
        <button class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left" data-action="click->accordion#toggle">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Who are the doctors I'll speak with?</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-plus text-blue-600 transform transition-transform duration-300"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="mt-4 hidden overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out opacity-0" data-accordion-target="content">
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            All MedGemma healthcare providers are board-certified and licensed in their respective specialties. Our network includes primary care physicians, pediatricians, dermatologists, psychiatrists, and other specialists from top medical institutions. Each provider undergoes a rigorous credentialing process and receives specialized training in telehealth best practices.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
        <button class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left" data-action="click->accordion#toggle">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Can MedGemma prescribe medications?</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-plus text-blue-600 transform transition-transform duration-300"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="mt-4 hidden overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out opacity-0" data-accordion-target="content">
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Yes, MedGemma doctors can prescribe a wide range of medications when medically necessary. Prescriptions are sent electronically to your preferred pharmacy for easy pickup. However, we cannot prescribe controlled substances or narcotics through our platform due to federal regulations. For these medications, we recommend seeing a provider in person.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
      <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
        <button class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left" data-action="click->accordion#toggle">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">How soon can I speak with a doctor?</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-plus text-blue-600 transform transition-transform duration-300"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="mt-4 hidden overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out opacity-0" data-accordion-target="content">
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            For urgent care needs, you can typically connect with a provider within 15-30 minutes. For specialist appointments, you can often schedule same-day or next-day consultations. Our platform shows real-time availability, allowing you to choose appointment times that work best for you. We also offer 24/7 access to medical professionals for urgent concerns.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="/help-center" class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors text-lg">
        View all FAQs
        <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

